{"tid":2516723,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"不等FB決定是否恢復帳號　侵仔先啟用新社交平台","createTime":"2021-05-04T23:43:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T23:45:08.000Z","uid":204533,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9bad6a7b88b74eb01586191ba9ac606aff8d10f6","tid":2516723,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T23:43:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/3nJTAC1SNFXQ1hLAS11drxYsALA=/760x427/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IPPPH2XD3NFLRP6WPJEBACUXZY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F3nJTAC1SNFXQ1hLAS11drxYsALA%3D%2F760x427%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIPPPH2XD3NFLRP6WPJEBACUXZY.jpg&h=195ada30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n社群媒體臉書（Facebook）獨立監督委員會即將在周三（5/5）對是否恢復美國前總統川普的帳號做出決定，但川普似乎不管臉書最後決定違和，他周二（5/4）推出最新社群平台，讓他能夠再透過網路與追隨者直接溝通。<br />\n<br />\n名為《From the Desk of Donald J. Trump》的平台，似由前川普競選陣營經理帕斯凱爾（Brad Parscale）創立的公司Campaign Nucleus支援，讓川普可以上傳留言、圖片和影片，但沒有讓網友「回覆」的功能。福斯新聞引述消息人士說，平台僅容許川普「單向溝通」。<br />\n<br />\n川普支持者於今年初衝擊國會期間，當時仍在任的川普在社群網站發片要求支持者回家，但同時聲稱大選舞弊，又說「我們愛你們，你們很特別，我們了解你們的感受」。影片遭fb、Twitter、YouTube刪除，該三大平台其後決定無限期暫停其帳號。<br />\n<br />\n臉書獨立監督委員會周三將就封殺令作出裁決，以決定維持還是撤銷禁令，並可能向fb提出建議。委員會的功能猶如最高法院，為敏感事項作決定，不會參與訂立規條。小組成員背景十分廣泛，包括來自全球各地的法學家、政策專家、記者等。<br />\n<br />\n專家指委員會的裁決將立下足以影響全球的先例。（國際中心／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"906e7282ecc07d60f75e01023dcc181b334d0cc1","tid":2516723,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T23:45:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210505/ALEN67Y4I5G4HE7QTA5XRYS4JQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210505%2FALEN67Y4I5G4HE7QTA5XRYS4JQ%2F&d=qHuNkoJYq05zO%2BFPSordK3Qc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=84df46c5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210505%2FALEN67Y4I5G4HE7QTA5XRYS4JQ%2F&h=ac038efa\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210505/ALEN67Y4I5G4HE7QTA5XRYS4JQ/</a>"}]}